Cell phone numbers are not to be used to determine if an inspector has a certain inspection for that day or time of inspection for your area. AGAIN, CELL PHONE NUMBERS ARE FOR RESOLVING BUILDING INSPECTION ISSUES ONLY! YOUR BUILDING INSPECTOR IS YOUR FIRST CONTACT, SECOND, CONTACT A CHIEF INSPECTOR. IF THIS DOES NOT GET YOUR SITUATION RESOLVED, PHILLIP CLIMER IS YOUR FINAL CONTACT. INSPECTION REQUEST CALL-IN: (972) 292-5386 Cut-off time for phone requests is 8:00 PM of the prior evening. ON-LINE REQUEST: Online requests made at: https://etrakit.friscotexas.gov/ Cut-off time for on-line requests is 7:00 AM the day of the requesting inspection. Building inspections: Cancel with the inspector assigned to the inspection. Camera and Right-of Way inspections: Cancel at (214)837-9603
